WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.488 align:middle line:90%


00:00:01.488 --> 00:00:04.464 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:04.464 --> 00:01:10.530 align:middle line:90%


00:01:10.530 --> 00:01:12.690 align:middle line:84%
>> Hello and welcome
to a "World of Wisdom."

00:01:12.690 --> 00:01:14.500 align:middle line:90%
I'm Carolyn Craft.

00:01:14.500 --> 00:01:17.930 align:middle line:84%
Edgar Cayce was a Christian
mystic and a pioneer

00:01:17.930 --> 00:01:19.550 align:middle line:90%
in holistic healing.

00:01:19.550 --> 00:01:23.930 align:middle line:84%
He not only was a
spiritual guide or guru

00:01:23.930 --> 00:01:26.660 align:middle line:84%
for a lot of his
people of that day,

00:01:26.660 --> 00:01:30.260 align:middle line:84%
but he taught us in this
day so much about how

00:01:30.260 --> 00:01:33.140 align:middle line:84%
we can tap into our
own inner wisdom,

00:01:33.140 --> 00:01:34.790 align:middle line:90%
our own spiritual guidance.

00:01:34.790 --> 00:01:38.570 align:middle line:84%
My guest today Dr. Mark Thurston
is the Executive Director

00:01:38.570 --> 00:01:40.730 align:middle line:90%
for the Edgar Cayce Foundation.

00:01:40.730 --> 00:01:45.050 align:middle line:84%
And he is an author, a lecturer,
and I think a psychologist.

00:01:45.050 --> 00:01:48.023 align:middle line:84%
And it's a wonderful for
you to be joining us today.

00:01:48.023 --> 00:01:48.940 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you, Carolyn.

00:01:48.940 --> 00:01:52.700 align:middle line:84%
>> We're going to zero in this
time together on this book,

00:01:52.700 --> 00:01:55.370 align:middle line:84%
"Synchronicity as
Spiritual Guidance."

00:01:55.370 --> 00:01:57.260 align:middle line:84%
One of the lines in
here is, "All of life

00:01:57.260 --> 00:02:00.850 align:middle line:84%
is working together to
give you little hints."

00:02:00.850 --> 00:02:03.440 align:middle line:84%
The intent underneath this
was to really help us all.

00:02:03.440 --> 00:02:06.200 align:middle line:84%
How has it helped your
own life in sorting out

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:07.880 align:middle line:90%
synchronicity events?

00:02:07.880 --> 00:02:10.340 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I think in many ways
spiritual guidance has shaped

00:02:10.340 --> 00:02:11.150 align:middle line:90%
my life.

00:02:11.150 --> 00:02:13.602 align:middle line:10%
At the critical
junctures of my life,

00:02:13.602 --> 00:02:15.560 align:middle line:10%
as many people could say
about their own lives,

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:19.400 align:middle line:10%
there have been little signs,
whether it came through a dream

00:02:19.400 --> 00:02:22.010 align:middle line:10%
or prompting at the
end of meditation,

00:02:22.010 --> 00:02:25.580 align:middle line:10%
or an event or a series of
events happening around you,

00:02:25.580 --> 00:02:27.500 align:middle line:10%
or perhaps, words
that someone says

00:02:27.500 --> 00:02:30.020 align:middle line:10%
that seemed to have wisdom
to them that didn't really

00:02:30.020 --> 00:02:33.890 align:middle line:10%
intend to be as profound as
they were heard by you to be.

00:02:33.890 --> 00:02:35.390 align:middle line:84%
And this is a book
that was really

00:02:35.390 --> 00:02:37.400 align:middle line:84%
meant to try to collect
some of those tools

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:40.920 align:middle line:84%
and some of those methods
into a handbook of sorts.

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:45.800 align:middle line:84%
It's also tied back into an
Eastern form of guidance,

00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:49.190 align:middle line:84%
an oracle called the Yijing,
which some of your viewers

00:02:49.190 --> 00:02:51.580 align:middle line:84%
may have worked with
in their own lives.

00:02:51.580 --> 00:02:53.630 align:middle line:84%
The Yijing is
thousands of years old,

00:02:53.630 --> 00:02:57.650 align:middle line:84%
and it involves 64
different life themes that

00:02:57.650 --> 00:03:01.910 align:middle line:84%
are created through the throwing
of coins or yarrow sticks,

00:03:01.910 --> 00:03:05.480 align:middle line:84%
and in a way, that seems
to be totally illogical,

00:03:05.480 --> 00:03:08.210 align:middle line:84%
one finds themselves
reading one of these 64 life

00:03:08.210 --> 00:03:11.270 align:middle line:84%
themes and the guidance and
the message that's there.

00:03:11.270 --> 00:03:14.810 align:middle line:84%
And I took those themes and
found in the Cayce material

00:03:14.810 --> 00:03:16.328 align:middle line:90%
those same principles.

00:03:16.328 --> 00:03:17.870 align:middle line:84%
And so in this book,
there's a chance

00:03:17.870 --> 00:03:19.790 align:middle line:84%
to work with this
form of divination

00:03:19.790 --> 00:03:21.800 align:middle line:84%
or this kind of an
oracle, but also

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:24.920 align:middle line:84%
bring in some of the words
of Edgar Cayce himself.

00:03:24.920 --> 00:03:27.920 align:middle line:10%
>> Maybe a little later to get
into specifically how we look

00:03:27.920 --> 00:03:29.390 align:middle line:10%
at the Yijing.

00:03:29.390 --> 00:03:34.940 align:middle line:10%
But tell us now, how do we
begin to develop the awareness

00:03:34.940 --> 00:03:38.600 align:middle line:10%
of synchronicity in our life?

00:03:38.600 --> 00:03:41.200 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, synchronicity is a term
that was coined by the great

00:03:41.200 --> 00:03:43.660 align:middle line:90%
Swiss psychiatrist Carl Jung.

00:03:43.660 --> 00:03:46.810 align:middle line:84%
And he felt that it
was a complementary law

00:03:46.810 --> 00:03:49.090 align:middle line:90%
to the law of cause and effect.

00:03:49.090 --> 00:03:52.150 align:middle line:84%
Like any good scientist, he saw
that cause and effect clearly

00:03:52.150 --> 00:03:54.650 align:middle line:90%
governs much of materiality.

00:03:54.650 --> 00:03:56.500 align:middle line:84%
But he felt, especially
from watching

00:03:56.500 --> 00:03:58.930 align:middle line:84%
the experiences in
his own life and those

00:03:58.930 --> 00:04:02.080 align:middle line:84%
of his patients or his
clients, that oftentimes, there

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:03.790 align:middle line:84%
was another
principle that seemed

00:04:03.790 --> 00:04:07.030 align:middle line:84%
to be at work of
meaningful coincidences,

00:04:07.030 --> 00:04:10.930 align:middle line:84%
where things seem to happen
two or three or four times

00:04:10.930 --> 00:04:12.490 align:middle line:84%
in a way that
matched each other,

00:04:12.490 --> 00:04:14.740 align:middle line:90%
but didn't cause each other.

00:04:14.740 --> 00:04:16.870 align:middle line:84%
And those kinds of
meaningful coincidences,

00:04:16.870 --> 00:04:20.560 align:middle line:84%
when they related to a personal
issue or some sole pattern

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:23.740 align:middle line:84%
that we're wrestling with, often
had a certain guidance quality

00:04:23.740 --> 00:04:24.770 align:middle line:90%
to it.

00:04:24.770 --> 00:04:26.820 align:middle line:84%
>> We also have in
developing our awareness,

00:04:26.820 --> 00:04:29.320 align:middle line:84%
I know I hear this a lot, too,
and in my own life, practice,

00:04:29.320 --> 00:04:30.240 align:middle line:90%
practice, practice.

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:34.600 align:middle line:84%
We begin to trust that
we are receiving guidance

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:36.670 align:middle line:84%
through the various
ways, don't we?

00:04:36.670 --> 00:04:38.990 align:middle line:84%
>> We do without
becoming superstitious.

00:04:38.990 --> 00:04:39.790 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:04:39.790 --> 00:04:43.750 align:middle line:84%
>> And our willingness to be
alert for inner and outer signs

00:04:43.750 --> 00:04:47.560 align:middle line:84%
to direct us and to guide
us shouldn't slip over

00:04:47.560 --> 00:04:51.160 align:middle line:84%
into an abandonment of our
own rationality and our common

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:52.480 align:middle line:90%
sense.

00:04:52.480 --> 00:04:54.590 align:middle line:84%
We become superstitious
if we say, well, I'm

00:04:54.590 --> 00:04:56.215 align:middle line:84%
going to do this
because a sign told me

00:04:56.215 --> 00:04:58.930 align:middle line:84%
I ought to be doing it,
rather than asking ourselves,

00:04:58.930 --> 00:05:02.770 align:middle line:84%
does it measure up to the best
I know to be doing in my life?

00:05:02.770 --> 00:05:05.920 align:middle line:84%
>> One clue I know my own
life, if I had to defend it,

00:05:05.920 --> 00:05:07.477 align:middle line:90%
then there's something not--

00:05:07.477 --> 00:05:09.310 align:middle line:84%
it's not really coming
from that true place,

00:05:09.310 --> 00:05:11.770 align:middle line:84%
when I feel that I've got
to explain it or defend it.

00:05:11.770 --> 00:05:15.160 align:middle line:84%
But when it's really
a synchronistic event,

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:18.710 align:middle line:90%
I know and trust it.

00:05:18.710 --> 00:05:20.890 align:middle line:90%
And I'm open for more, too.

00:05:20.890 --> 00:05:23.530 align:middle line:84%
>> I'm a systematic enough
person that I've tried

00:05:23.530 --> 00:05:26.830 align:middle line:84%
to assemble certain steps where
a person could work with either

00:05:26.830 --> 00:05:29.510 align:middle line:84%
dream guidance or these kind
of outer signs or meditation

00:05:29.510 --> 00:05:30.310 align:middle line:90%
guidance.

00:05:30.310 --> 00:05:32.045 align:middle line:84%
>> You've got an
eight step formula.

00:05:32.045 --> 00:05:33.920 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, maybe we could
go over that briefly.

00:05:33.920 --> 00:05:34.720 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:37.700 align:middle line:84%
>> The first step is to get
real clear about your core value

00:05:37.700 --> 00:05:38.500 align:middle line:90%
in life.

00:05:38.500 --> 00:05:41.740 align:middle line:84%
Cayce usually call that
setting a spiritual ideal.

00:05:41.740 --> 00:05:43.330 align:middle line:84%
But it's a matter
of asking yourself,

00:05:43.330 --> 00:05:45.880 align:middle line:84%
do I put peace at the
center of my life or love

00:05:45.880 --> 00:05:48.880 align:middle line:84%
or oneness or creativity
or joyfulness?

00:05:48.880 --> 00:05:51.150 align:middle line:84%
What's the core
value for your life?

00:05:51.150 --> 00:05:52.900 align:middle line:84%
We're going to use
that as a measuring rod

00:05:52.900 --> 00:05:54.385 align:middle line:84%
as we move through
the other steps.

00:05:54.385 --> 00:05:55.185 align:middle line:90%
>> You also give--

00:05:55.185 --> 00:05:57.940 align:middle line:84%
I'll just stop you
just for one second.

00:05:57.940 --> 00:06:01.773 align:middle line:84%
You also give a way to
identify your core value, which

00:06:01.773 --> 00:06:02.690 align:middle line:90%
is real key, isn't it?

00:06:02.690 --> 00:06:05.380 align:middle line:84%
>> By going back to some of
your peak spiritual experiences.

00:06:05.380 --> 00:06:06.180 align:middle line:90%
>> Exactly.

00:06:06.180 --> 00:06:08.770 align:middle line:84%
>> Those have been hints to
you about your best self.

00:06:08.770 --> 00:06:11.850 align:middle line:84%
And if we'll recall those
peak moments in our lives,

00:06:11.850 --> 00:06:13.600 align:middle line:84%
they often give us an
inkling about what's

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:16.150 align:middle line:84%
really at the core of
our own spiritual nature.

00:06:16.150 --> 00:06:18.700 align:middle line:84%
>> An example of a
core spiritual value,

00:06:18.700 --> 00:06:20.142 align:middle line:90%
a core value would be like what?

00:06:20.142 --> 00:06:21.850 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, some of the
things I just named.

00:06:21.850 --> 00:06:24.220 align:middle line:84%
You could set peace
as a core value,

00:06:24.220 --> 00:06:26.932 align:middle line:84%
or fairness or
joyfulness or love,

00:06:26.932 --> 00:06:28.390 align:middle line:84%
or if you need a
few more words, it

00:06:28.390 --> 00:06:32.350 align:middle line:84%
could be a phrase,
peaceful creativity,

00:06:32.350 --> 00:06:33.460 align:middle line:90%
oneness with the Buddha.

00:06:33.460 --> 00:06:34.960 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we can come
up with anything

00:06:34.960 --> 00:06:35.980 align:middle line:90%
that feels right to us.

00:06:35.980 --> 00:06:37.810 align:middle line:84%
>> And would you just
have one core value,

00:06:37.810 --> 00:06:39.220 align:middle line:90%
or would you have several?

00:06:39.220 --> 00:06:42.370 align:middle line:84%
>> There are certainly
supportive values and behaviors

00:06:42.370 --> 00:06:44.200 align:middle line:90%
that grow out of that.

00:06:44.200 --> 00:06:45.940 align:middle line:84%
Edgar Cayce's his
recommendation was

00:06:45.940 --> 00:06:49.370 align:middle line:84%
having a kind of focal point
or a kind of central value.

00:06:49.370 --> 00:06:51.730 align:middle line:84%
And that's open to
growth and development

00:06:51.730 --> 00:06:54.650 align:middle line:90%
as the months and years go by.

00:06:54.650 --> 00:06:57.340 align:middle line:84%
>> So after you've clarified
your spiritual value?

00:06:57.340 --> 00:07:00.220 align:middle line:84%
>> Second step is to
formulate the question.

00:07:00.220 --> 00:07:02.140 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes we want
to skip over that step,

00:07:02.140 --> 00:07:04.223 align:middle line:84%
because we say, well, I
know what the question is.

00:07:04.223 --> 00:07:07.180 align:middle line:84%
But actually writing it down
and getting clear what it is you

00:07:07.180 --> 00:07:07.980 align:middle line:90%
want to know.

00:07:07.980 --> 00:07:09.140 align:middle line:90%
What's your question?

00:07:09.140 --> 00:07:11.020 align:middle line:84%
Once you've got
that written down,

00:07:11.020 --> 00:07:13.780 align:middle line:84%
then a third step before you
start looking for guidance

00:07:13.780 --> 00:07:17.380 align:middle line:84%
is to do your homework
with your conscious mind.

00:07:17.380 --> 00:07:19.570 align:middle line:90%
Collect the facts.

00:07:19.570 --> 00:07:21.280 align:middle line:84%
Collect all the
information you can

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:23.830 align:middle line:90%
at a conscious, rational level.

00:07:23.830 --> 00:07:26.950 align:middle line:84%
And then at step four, make
a tentative decision, just

00:07:26.950 --> 00:07:30.640 align:middle line:84%
a provisional decision
that uses rationality,

00:07:30.640 --> 00:07:33.300 align:middle line:84%
the analytical
mind, common sense.

00:07:33.300 --> 00:07:35.920 align:middle line:84%
And you say, without having
yet gotten any guidance

00:07:35.920 --> 00:07:39.580 align:middle line:84%
on this, what do I think
the best answer probably is?

00:07:39.580 --> 00:07:42.670 align:middle line:84%
But before you act on it,
then the remaining steps

00:07:42.670 --> 00:07:46.270 align:middle line:84%
involve working with
inner and outer guidance.

00:07:46.270 --> 00:07:49.400 align:middle line:84%
So with step five, we
begin to watch our dreams.

00:07:49.400 --> 00:07:52.660 align:middle line:84%
We begin to ask at the end of
a prayer, meditation session

00:07:52.660 --> 00:07:54.610 align:middle line:90%
for some type of a prompting.

00:07:54.610 --> 00:07:58.180 align:middle line:84%
We begin to watch for
signs in the outer world.

00:07:58.180 --> 00:08:01.540 align:middle line:84%
We begin to perhaps
consult with a friend

00:08:01.540 --> 00:08:03.822 align:middle line:90%
or professional intuitive.

00:08:03.822 --> 00:08:05.530 align:middle line:84%
There are many different
ways, consulting

00:08:05.530 --> 00:08:09.730 align:middle line:84%
an Yijing or the runes or
many of these other oracles.

00:08:09.730 --> 00:08:12.550 align:middle line:84%
And then as we collect
this information,

00:08:12.550 --> 00:08:15.280 align:middle line:84%
and we begin to assemble
it, the next step

00:08:15.280 --> 00:08:20.620 align:middle line:84%
is then to formulate what we
feel like is a guided decision.

00:08:20.620 --> 00:08:22.900 align:middle line:84%
Now we're beginning to
put together rationality

00:08:22.900 --> 00:08:24.808 align:middle line:90%
and intuition as well.

00:08:24.808 --> 00:08:26.350 align:middle line:84%
And as we come up
with something that

00:08:26.350 --> 00:08:29.920 align:middle line:84%
feels like a guided decision,
that in step number seven,

00:08:29.920 --> 00:08:32.140 align:middle line:84%
we want to measure
that and make sure

00:08:32.140 --> 00:08:35.030 align:middle line:84%
it's consistent with
our spiritual ideal.

00:08:35.030 --> 00:08:37.010 align:middle line:84%
And this is just sort
of a silly example,

00:08:37.010 --> 00:08:40.610 align:middle line:84%
but one time at a workshop
on meditation for guidance,

00:08:40.610 --> 00:08:42.679 align:middle line:90%
a woman went into meditation.

00:08:42.679 --> 00:08:44.277 align:middle line:90%
She had a question.

00:08:44.277 --> 00:08:46.610 align:middle line:84%
The workshop leader said,
now, at the end of meditation,

00:08:46.610 --> 00:08:50.095 align:middle line:84%
pose your question inwardly
and listen for an answer.

00:08:50.095 --> 00:08:51.470 align:middle line:84%
And she said later
that she heard

00:08:51.470 --> 00:08:55.340 align:middle line:84%
a little voice that said, why
don't you just kill yourself?

00:08:55.340 --> 00:08:57.680 align:middle line:84%
Now, she asked the workshop
presenter afterwards,

00:08:57.680 --> 00:08:59.400 align:middle line:90%
what should I do?

00:08:59.400 --> 00:09:01.670 align:middle line:84%
And if she doesn't
have a step in there

00:09:01.670 --> 00:09:05.840 align:middle line:84%
where she takes what looks to
be something coming from within,

00:09:05.840 --> 00:09:09.900 align:middle line:84%
but then ask does it measure
up to my spiritual ideal,

00:09:09.900 --> 00:09:12.410 align:middle line:84%
then she's going to act on
something that surely is not

00:09:12.410 --> 00:09:13.900 align:middle line:90%
coming from her best self.

00:09:13.900 --> 00:09:14.240 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:16.698 align:middle line:84%
>> Surely that's coming from
her subconscious and some kind

00:09:16.698 --> 00:09:19.400 align:middle line:84%
of a fear or insecurity
or self-doubt.

00:09:19.400 --> 00:09:21.740 align:middle line:84%
>> What did she do with
that then at that point?

00:09:21.740 --> 00:09:23.610 align:middle line:84%
She measures it
against her ideal.

00:09:23.610 --> 00:09:26.540 align:middle line:84%
>> And if it doesn't measure up,
then you go back and you look

00:09:26.540 --> 00:09:28.420 align:middle line:90%
for guidance further.

00:09:28.420 --> 00:09:29.220 align:middle line:90%
We all--

00:09:29.220 --> 00:09:31.140 align:middle line:90%
>> And explore that message?

00:09:31.140 --> 00:09:32.690 align:middle line:84%
And you would explore
that message--

00:09:32.690 --> 00:09:34.190 align:middle line:84%
>> Where did that
message come from?

00:09:34.190 --> 00:09:36.620 align:middle line:84%
That could be part of the
clearing out or the cleansing

00:09:36.620 --> 00:09:39.710 align:middle line:84%
process in order to allow
the more accurate intuition

00:09:39.710 --> 00:09:41.120 align:middle line:90%
to come through.

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:42.890 align:middle line:84%
I always encourage
people to work, though,

00:09:42.890 --> 00:09:45.260 align:middle line:90%
with multiple forms of guidance.

00:09:45.260 --> 00:09:46.700 align:middle line:90%
Don't just look at your dreams.

00:09:46.700 --> 00:09:48.800 align:middle line:90%
Don't just consult the Yijing.

00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:50.900 align:middle line:84%
Don't just watch for
synchronistic signs.

00:09:50.900 --> 00:09:53.120 align:middle line:84%
Don't just meditate
for guidance.

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:55.970 align:middle line:84%
Try to get two or
three or four streams,

00:09:55.970 --> 00:09:59.030 align:middle line:84%
and then see if they
begin to dovetail.

00:09:59.030 --> 00:10:00.800 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes like my
fingers fitting

00:10:00.800 --> 00:10:02.390 align:middle line:84%
together, one
builds on the other,

00:10:02.390 --> 00:10:04.970 align:middle line:84%
and you get a fabric where you
get a bigger picture, a more

00:10:04.970 --> 00:10:07.830 align:middle line:90%
comprehensive understanding.

00:10:07.830 --> 00:10:10.570 align:middle line:84%
>> So in the eight
steps, we're asking--

00:10:10.570 --> 00:10:12.560 align:middle line:84%
>> The eighth we need
to add, which is to act

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:13.440 align:middle line:90%
on the guidance.

00:10:13.440 --> 00:10:14.050 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:10:14.050 --> 00:10:14.960 align:middle line:90%
>> Go ahead.

00:10:14.960 --> 00:10:18.380 align:middle line:84%
