refines that guidance.

00:10:53.060 --> 00:10:56.640 align:middle line:84%
And so it's, in a sense, a
flow that keeps recycling.

00:10:56.640 --> 00:11:00.980 align:middle line:84%
>> And Mark, it appears
that it's continually asking

00:11:00.980 --> 00:11:06.770 align:middle line:84%
the individual to go to the
their inner self to really

00:11:06.770 --> 00:11:09.980 align:middle line:84%
check in right there,
moment by moment.

00:11:09.980 --> 00:11:12.020 align:middle line:84%
