eating or watching the evening

00:11:31.400 --> 00:11:34.340 align:middle line:84%
news or looking at the
newspaper, time for quiet to

00:11:34.340 --> 00:11:36.980 align:middle line:90%
tune in.

00:11:36.980 --> 00:11:41.762 align:middle line:84%
