00:11:47.700 --> 00:11:48.950 align:middle line:90%
>> Edgar Cayce was asked that.

00:11:48.950 --> 00:11:50.090 align:middle line:90%
>> We give ideas.

00:11:50.090 --> 00:11:52.700 align:middle line:84%
