element to the dream.

00:12:13.190 --> 00:12:15.510 align:middle line:84%
I might be willing to
share the dream with you,

00:12:15.510 --> 00:12:17.120 align:middle line:84%
and if you immediately
give me signs

00:12:17.120 --> 00:12:19.825 align:middle line:84%
