it being about you at all,

00:12:19.825 --> 00:12:21.200 align:middle line:84%
I'm not going to
force the issue.

00:12:21.200 --> 00:12:22.530 align:middle line:90%
I'll back off.

00:12:22.530 --> 00:12:24.410 align:middle line:84%
But if you show that
you'd like to explore

00:12:24.410 --> 00:12:26.540 align:middle line:84%
that it may be a
psychic dream, I'll

00:12:26.540 --> 00:12:28.130 align:middle line:84%
take it as far as
you want to go.

00:12:28.130 --> 00:12:29.420 align:middle line:90%
>> And would we always know?

00:12:29.420 --> 00:12:32.600 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes we may not even
be sure if it is about me

00:12:32.600 --> 00:12:37.820 align:middle line:84%
